          "content": "The LINCE team wants to tighten a safety guard before automated trades are sent. Identify where the change should likely be made, what callers or dependencies may be affected, and what tests or checks should be added before release. Respond with JSON: {\"change_areas\":[\"...\"],\"affected_dependencies\":[\"...\"],\"test_plan\":[\"...\"],\"risks\":[\"...\"],\"summary\":\"...\"}."
